# TRMG -True Random Mnemonic Generator

## Generate mnemonic
You need 3 dice:
- 2 dice with 16 faces, we will call it First and Second
- 1 dice with 8 faces, we will call it Third

Throws dices 12 or 24 times in order to generate the words, for each roll you can read the corresponding word in the following table.

Index is calculate as (Fist-1)*2^7+(Second-1)*2^3+(Third-1).
